headline: Is Alliant Energy Fairly Priced After Recent Gains and Clean Energy Investment Focus?
summary: Wondering if Alliant Energy at around $64.81 is still a smart buy, or if most of the upside has already been priced in? Let us break down what the numbers are really saying about its value. The stock has dipped about 2.4% over the last week and 3.2% over the last month, but it is still up 10.8% year to date and 47.6% over the past five years, which hints at a steady long term story rather than a quick trade.
